{"tid":2190044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網民號召 9.6 九龍大遊行　多間傳媒引消息：警部署 2000 警力應付","createTime":"2020-09-05T10:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T16:21:56.000Z","uid":312363,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"125f897b19fa659b7639a604e1d6c69079e14147","tid":2190044,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"有網民發起明日（ 6 日）九龍大遊行，反對《港區國安法》、健康碼及押後立法會選舉。多間傳媒今日引述消息，指警方已部署逾 2,000 警力應付。另外，昨晚有網媒拍攝到工人在旺角西洋菜南街行人路，為地磚搽膠水，《立場》記者今日再到旺角視察，地磚已用膠水封好，殘留少量膠水漬黏住泥沙。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨（4 日）已在 FB 發帖，指明日遊行未獲警方的不反對通知書，參與組織或煽惑他人參與未經批准集結或非法集結，均有可能觸犯《公安條例》，疫情下亦有可能違反「限聚令」。<br />\n<br />\n警方今日再在 FB 發帖，指有人繼續在網上鼓吹他人參與遊行，聲言要「重燃戰火」、「絕地反擊」，強調明日會在西九龍一帶部署足夠警力，其他警區亦會提高戒備，警告將會「迅速果斷執法，適時拘捕，絕不手軟。」多家傳媒引述「消息」指，警方已部署 2000 警力，應對明日可能出現的遊行示威。"},{"pid":"d6ea3bb3990f412b8294a766d0496056c30e6f48","tid":2190044,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"limegreen\">2000隻曱甴</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e985153fc0285c42c43bfefb4a7e812ba9c4a03","tid":2190044,"uid":277054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mnj6ea0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnj6ea0.jpg&h=ac49e904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tkhkQ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tkhkQ0.jpg&h=cd48befc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXg024m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXg024m.jpg&h=51c2badd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVAMYCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVAMYCG.jpg&h=90e744f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8525cde47b0a4ef82cb68f16609acdb894ee6c5","tid":2190044,"uid":346260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05